{
  "stem": "19111.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Life became a-- daily news that came in became almost a frightening experience every single day, because every single day, we got these reports from what is happening in the ghetto, how they kept still taking people to the slaughter.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we thought that any morning, any day that'll come, they'll come and get us just as well.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were trapped, and we were helpless.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the fear of death, we faced death every single moment of every single day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, two of them were caught in the roundup of Jews and killed in Ponary.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "None of them made it to the Kailis.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were killed before the establishment of Kailis.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we continued to live there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some of the elder people tried to get some semblance of-- of diversion, so to divert our minds a little bit.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had a little-- formed a little class for the children secretly where they taught us a little math, a little literature, and very quietly we sang some little songs.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we tried to pass the time away like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember, but they were all killed, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I probably-- not at the moment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they-- they tried to make the children feel a litter better, to get their mind off the fear and the helplessness that we have [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It worked somewhat, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It helped for an evening, if we got a little bit at that moment of the dangers, and the threat, and-- and all the killing and all the-- what was going on in the ghetto and all that, it was good to have a little bit of a diversion.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's what they intended to do, especially for the young.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had-- there was a time in 1944.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
